				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">blargg was subject to <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Off-by-one_error" class="postlink">off-by-one error</a> when counting bits, but he actually said that there's 15 bits to the LFSR (14-0) because <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Linear_feedback_shift_register#Some_polynomials_for_maximal_LFSRs" class="postlink">it'd have required 2 more taps for 16 bits</a>. And anyways, with 16 bits the maximum sequence would have been 65535 bits, which would be incorrect.</div>

